[I] C library for accessing the PostgreSQL parser outside of the server

[T] libpg_query is a C library for accessing the PostgreSQL parser outside of
[T] the server. This library uses the actual PostgreSQL server source to parse
[T] SQL queries and return the internal PostgreSQL parse tree.

[U] https://github.com/pganalyze/libpg_query

